snippet.title: Content Drop: Rejects Unite | Official Trailer - Warhammer 40,000: Darktide
snippet.description:
Rejects Unite is the latest update for Darktide, offering new content, including new missions, a new enemy, a revamped earnable cosmetics shop, and more!

Learn more about the content update: https://bit.ly/45udXvY
